{"tid":2199593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港體育學院主席林大輝： 職員教練運動員約1000人需要未來兩日去全民檢疫 之後才決定體院重開日子 不參加會令運動員不安","createTime":"2020-09-12T10:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T10:29:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7f875594b27ed6ba343d3b1d484cebc13ee46f","tid":2199593,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"香港體育學院因疫情封鎖已46日，今午（12日）宣布安排體院上下約1000人，在未來兩日接受政府安排的新冠病毒測試，並會之後持續每星期檢測，視乎結果決定體院重開日子。<br />\n<br />\n體院自7月29日起再度封關，但第三波疫情近日緩和，主席林大輝稱前日已就體院全民檢測拍板，而由政府安排是最快捷方便的做法：「最好的防疫措施就是檢測，是基本要求，希望全部甲級運動員、職員及教練都做檢測，得到數字才能考慮怎樣重新開放體院。」<br />\n<br />\n政府將負責今次檢測及指定化驗機構，林大輝稱目標是體院上下約1000人，不擔心反應未如理想：「相信經過解釋，經過了解後，他們會參加。假如教練不參加，他的行為會令運動員感到不安，我想大家會識得權衡當中的輕重。」對於有體院職員質疑檢測為政府「湊數」，亦有運動員質疑在院內封閉逾一個月，仍要接受檢測的原因，林大輝稱體院亦接受合格的私人檢測機構證明，確診個案將由政府處理，強調體院無責任為政府全民檢測「湊數」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20200912/s00006/1599901640448/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e9%ab%94%e9%99%a2%e6%98%8e%e8%b5%b7%e6%aa%a2%e6%b8%ac%e5%8d%83%e4%ba%ba%e4%bb%a5%e6%b1%ba%e5%ae%9a%e8%a7%a3%e5%b0%81%e5%ae%89%e6%8e%92-%e5%90%a6%e8%aa%8d%e7%82%ba%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e6%b9%8a%e6%95%b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20200912%2Fs00006%2F1599901640448%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e9%25ab%2594%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%2598%258e%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%25b8%25ac%25e5%258d%2583%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%25b1%25ba%25e5%25ae%259a%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e5%25b0%2581%25e5%25ae%2589%25e6%258e%2592-%25e5%2590%25a6%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%2582%25ba%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c%25e6%25b9%258a%25e6%2595%25b8&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9fyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=d3cb7ca4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20200912%2Fs00006%2F1599901640448%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e9%25ab%2594%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%2598%258e%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%25b8%25ac%25e5%258d%2583%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%25b1%25ba%25e5%25ae%259a%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e5%25b0%2581%25e5%25ae%2589%25e6%258e%2592-%25e5%2590%25a6%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%2582%25ba%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c%25e6%25b9%258a%25e6%2595%25b8&h=5b457976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20200912/s00006/1599901640448/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e9%ab%94%e9%99%a2%e6%98%8e%e8%b5%b7%e6%aa%a2%e6%b8%ac%e5%8d%83%e4%ba%ba%e4%bb%a5%e6%b1%ba%e5%ae%9a%e8%a7%a3%e5%b0%81%e5%ae%89%e6%8e%92-%e5%90%a6%e8%aa%8d%e7%82%ba%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e6%b9%8a%e6%95%b8</a>"},{"pid":"57b328bcccfb7fa49fb82242dce2d60c99ef81c7","tid":2199593,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e812f8cb1635ef6be8e3c02785f65b2b7b0fcd09","tid":2199593,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:24:32.000Z","msg":"驗完一次孕無中招就可以永久瘋狂中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a50ffb9f83f6b9beae14115a41435ddfdee307","tid":2199593,"uid":60539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚開囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f1c0031950451bc95723788d64aa2c8029cde5","tid":2199593,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"有班喺體育隔離咗成個月嘅運動員都要驗？<br />\n就算帶病入去嘅，都一早好返晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas